text: KWQR (92.5 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Willcox, Arizona. The station is owned by Mark Lucke, through licensee Versailles Community Broadcasting, Inc., and airs a classic hits format described as "X-Wave". The station was assigned the KWQR call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on March 9, 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * WQR Category:Radio stations established in 2017 Category:2017 establishments in Arizona Category:Classic hits radio stations in the United States Category:Cochise County, Arizona
